@host = http://localhost:5256

### Get all service requests
GET {{host}}/api/servicerequests
Accept: application/json

### Get service request by id
GET {{host}}/api/servicerequests/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a service request
POST {{host}}/api/servicerequests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New user needs Power BI access",
  "description": "A finance department user needs access to the monthly sales dashboard.",
  "category": "Reporting",
  "priority": "Medium",
  "status": "Open"
}

### Update service request
PUT {{host}}/api/servicerequests/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New user needs Power BI access",
  "description": "A finance department user needs access to the monthly sales dashboard.",
  "category": "Reporting",
  "priority": "Medium",
  "status": "InProgress"
}

### Update service request status
PATCH {{host}}/api/servicerequests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

### Get service request status history
GET {{host}}/api/servicerequests/1/status-history
Accept: application/json